entry.summary:
Vendor: STARMAXDESIGN
Type:
Price: 0.00

Metal mesh materials are generally aluminum alloy, stainless steel, and copper wire mesh with good weather resistance. They are often used in protective nets, walls, fences, etc. in construction projects. Through designers' inspiration, metal mesh materials are widely used as landscape art installations and building exterior finishes. In interior design, metal mesh materials have more options and are more widely used. They can be used as maintenance partitions, stair railings, decorative materials, furniture materials, etc Metal mesh can effectively adjust light and heat comfort in buildings, form adequate ventilation, and prevent hot air from gathering for a long time. It is a decorative material that can transmit light, ventilation, and perspective.
